Marjorie Montgomery https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marjorie_Montgomery 0 Marjorie Montgomery (born May 27, 1912) is an American former child dancer and actress. She appeared in vaudeville and later in motion pictures, before becoming a noted fashion designer. Marjorie_Montgomery ( born May_27_,_1912 ) is an_American_former_child_dancer_and_actress .
